snippet.title: Enchanted Portals - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready for the highly anticipated release of our game on both PC and consoles this year!

You can already add it to your wish list on PC using the links provided. 

https://store.epicgames.com/es-ES/p/enchanted-portals-65ca68

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2444350/Enchanted_Portals/

Stay tuned for more exciting details about the console version coming soon!
